    <item>
      <title>日元大幅上涨后，日本央行利率审查引发干预猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/yen-strengthens-2-against-dollar-in-aftermath-of-us-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日本央行与交易员进行所谓的利率检查，日元周五出现波动，这强化了人们对日本央行周四干预市场以支撑日元的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/yen-strengthens-2-against-dollar-in-aftermath-of-us-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 12:52:19 GMT</pubDate>
